description:
I will explain how I came across parallel processing in Python, the problem-solving process, the library I used, and how to use it.

Kim Hyun-woo
I am a developer with 6 years of experience. I started working as a backend engineer in earnest in 2020. I mainly used Java, and recently joined OnePredict and started working with Python, Flask, SQLAlchemy, etc., and I am learning about the charm of Python.
title: Parallel Processing in Python
